  "content": "## Task 12: Full Pipeline Integration Test\n\n        store.insert(&e).await.unwrap();\n    }\n\n    // Create pipeline without generator (context-only)\n    let pipeline = corvia_kernel::create_rag_pipeline(\n        store, engine, None, None, &config,\n    );\n\n    // Test context() mode\n    let response = pipeline.context(\"topic 0\", \"test-scope\", None).await.unwrap();\n    assert!(response.answer.is_none());\n    assert!(response.context.metrics.sources_included > 0);\n    assert!(response.context.context.contains(\"[1]\")); // has citation markers\n    assert!(response.trace.retrieval.retriever_name == \"vector\");\n    assert!(response.trace.generation.is_none());\n    assert!(response.trace.total_latency_ms < 5000);\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2: Run it**\n\nRun: `cargo test --test rag_e2e_test -- --nocapture` (or however the test is registered)\nExpected: PASS\n\n**Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add crates/tests/integration/rag_e2e_test.rs crates/corvia-cli/Cargo.toml\ngit commit -m \"test(m3.2): RAG pipeline e2e integration test\"\n```\n\n---\n",
